metadata.name: The Finance Bull: Revolution - Original
metadata.description: Purchase and ownership of this NFT ensures the right of the ownership of the original physical artwork The Finance Bull: Revolution. The NFT acts as a valid certificate ensuring the authenticity of the physical artwork which shall be provided together with the NFT. In essence, the composition signifies the moment the establishement recognizes the true disruptive potential of Bitcoin. Such a disruptive force will not go unnoticed, or without a fight.
